⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Midna
node ZEL · ZEL · ⟦Midna:ZEL:9e73ae⟧

WHO   — Midna — the Twilight Princess
WHAT  — The exiled queen of the Twilight Realm — a being of the in-between, who rides the wolf the Hero has become and steers him through the dark toward the throne that was stolen.
WHERE — ZEL · The Legend of Zelda  Framework inputs: The Legend of Zelda (the saga entire)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because a throne was usurped and a people enslaved; because the Twilight and the light were never meant to be one realm's prison; because pride that begins as self-interest can become, in the end, a willingness to give everything.
HOW   — By shadow-magic and the fused power on her brow, by riding wolf-Link as guide and rider both, by cunning and sharp tongue and a courage she hides behind mischief — and by the final, breaking choice to set things right.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am the dusk between your worlds — exiled queen, impish guide, the shadow that chooses, in the end, the light.

